SELECT ORDER_ID, ORDER_STATUS, CUST_NAME, PERSON_FIRSTNAME, PERSON_LASTNAME, CUSTSITE_NAME FROM orders JOIN customers on orders.CUST_ID = customers.CUST_ID JOIN persons on persons.PERSON_ID = orders.PERSON_ID JOIN customersites on orders.CUSTSITE_ID = customersites.CUSTSITE_ID
SELECT ART_ID, ART_DESCRIPTION, ART_PRICE, ART_STOCK, ART_PRODUCED FROM articles WHERE ART_TYPE = 'PRODUCT'
SELECT a1.ART_ID, a2.ART_DESCRIPTION FROM articles a1 JOIN bom b1 on b1.BOM_PARENT = a1.ART_ID JOIN articles a2 on a2.ART_ID = b1.BOM_CHILD WHERE a2.ART_TYPE= 'SERVICE'

SELECT ORDERDET_ID, ORDERDET_STATUS, CUSTPROJ_ID, articles.ART_ID, ART_DESCRIPTION, QUANTITY, EXPECTED_DELIVERY_DATE, CONFIRMED_DELIVERY_DATE, DELIVERY_DATE FROM orderdetails JOIN articles on orderdetails.ART_ID = articles.ART_ID WHERE ORDER_ID = [[orderID]]
select ORDER_ID from orders where CUST_ID = [[customerID]] and PERSON_ID = [[personID]] and CUSTSITE_ID = [[siteID]];

SELECT a1.ART_ID, a1.ART_DESCRIPTION, a1.ART_PRICE FROM articles a1 JOIN bom b1 on b1.BOM_CHILD = a1.ART_ID JOIN articles a2 on a2.ART_ID = b1.BOM_PARENT WHERE a1.ART_TYPE = 'SERVICE' and a2.ART_ID = [[articleID]]
select ART_STOCK from articles where ART_DESCRIPTION = [[articleDescription]]

SELECT articles.ART_ID, SUPPLIER_NAME, ARTDEL_PRICE FROM articles join articlesuppliers on articlesuppliers.ART_ID = articles.ART_ID join suppliers on suppliers.SUPPLIER_ID = articlesuppliers.SUPPLIER_ID WHERE ART_TYPE = 'PRODUCT' AND articles.ART_ID = [[articleID]]
UPDATE [dbo].[articles] SET [ART_STOCK] = [[newStock]] WHERE [[articleDescription]] NOT IN ('MAINTENANCE', 'INSTALLATION') AND ART_DESCRIPTION = [[articleDescription]]
UPDATE orderdetails SET ORDERDET_STATUS = [[status]] WHERE ORDERDET_ID = [[orderDetID]]
UPDATE orders SET ORDER_STATUS = [[status]] WHERE ORDER_ID = [[orderID]]
